reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I got these for functionality, but fell in love at how cute they are! I was looking for a set of 2 - 4, but they all seemed a little too young for me. I also looked at the plain ones, but hey even Grammy’s get to have a little fun. :) These are perfect! I took a few I liked and left the rest up to my daughters to fight over. There are famous Seattle brand coffee cups, boba teas and fun donuts with sprinkles and ear buds! In all you get 12 total caps at a price that I found to be lower than other sets of 4 - 6. All of the designs are cute and vivid and the silicone feels very durable. Buy these and you will have one for all your cups and even a BFF-teas cap to give to your own BFF! Great value and lots of smiles!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These Hello Kitty straw covers are just as cute in person and fit nicely over my silicone straws. So helpful when I'm carrying my drink out to the car, so the liquid is coming out anymore. The selection and price are amazing. Plus, there's enough to share with friends and family. Great value!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are really cute. The younger grand kids are able to remove them so they can drink from the straw. They stop the drink from spilling out of the straw when the cup is tipped over. They are pretty strong and don't break when they keep getting removed.
